title: Top Moscow Doctor Tests Positive for Coronavirus After Shaking Putin's Hand
description: The head of Moscow’s top hospital for Chinese coronavirus patients announced on Tuesday he had tested positive for the virus less than a week after meeting and shaking hands with Russian President Vladimir Putin.
